'''奧菲利亞·露西·拉維邦德'''（{{Lang-en|'''Ophelia Lucy Lovibond'''}}，{{bd|1986年|2月19日}}）是一位英國影視女演員。

==早年生活==
奧菲利亞·拉維邦德出生於[[倫敦|倫敦]]。

== 職業 ==
奧菲利亞·拉維邦德於早年以參與英國電視劇和電影為主，於2009電影《{{le|無處的男孩|Nowhere_Boy}}》<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117941505.html?categoryid=31&cs=1|title=Review: 'Nowhere Boy'|work=Variety|accessdate=2014-08-16|archive-date=2009-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091104120509/http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117941505.html?categoryid=31&cs=1|dead-url=no}}</ref> 和電視劇《{{le|FM (電視劇)|FM (TV series)|FM}}》<ref>[http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1385167/ FM] {{Wayback|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1385167/ |date=20210201123636 }} at the Internet Movie Database</ref>當配角後為人所留意。在2010電影《{{le|4.3.2.1}}》擔當主角之一<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.empireonline.com/reviews/reviewcomplete.asp?FID=136565 |title=Empire's 4.3.2.1 Movie Review<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2014-08-16 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924134852/http://www.empireonline.com/reviews/reviewcomplete.asp?FID=136565 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。期後拉維邦德開始參與荷里活電影，如在2011電影《[[飯飯之交|飯飯之交]]》飾演男主角亞當的前女友凡妮莎、《[[波普先生的企鵝|波普先生的企鵝]]》飾演波特先生的助理皮皮、《[[雷神索爾2：黑暗世界|雷神索爾2：黑暗世界]]》和《[[银河护卫队_(电影)|星際異攻隊]]》飾演「收藏者」坦納里·帝凡的女僕卡琳娜<ref name="GotGRole">{{cite web|url=http://comicbook.com/blog/2013/11/08/thor-the-dark-world-after-the-credits-detailed-explanation/|title=Thor: The Dark World After The Credits Detailed Explanation|last=Blackmon|first=Joe|publisher=Comicbook.com|date=November 8, 2013|accessdate=November 10, 2013|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20131110065111/http://comicbook.com/blog/2013/11/08/thor-the-dark-world-after-the-credits-detailed-explanation/|archivedate=2013-11-10|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="GotG">{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/guardians-galaxy-adds-one-more-443087 |title='Guardians of the Galaxy' Adds One More to Cast (Exclusive) |first=Borys |last=Kit |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=April 22, 2013 |accessdate=April 22, 2013 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6G4wrfuVd?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/guardians-galaxy-adds-one-more-443087 |archivedate=2013-04-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

於2010年及2011年，分別被評為世界最美麗臉孔第65位<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.tccandler.com/100-most-beautiful-faces-2010/ |title=The 2010 Most Beautiful Faces List |access-date=2014-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130720001429/http://www.tccandler.com/100-most-beautiful-faces-2010/ |archive-date=2013-07-20 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>及全球百位最美女性第76位<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://fightnetwork.com/news/9731:arianny-celeste-makes-top-99-most-desirable-women-list/ |title=Top 99 Most Desirable Women of 2011 List |access-date=2014-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140819083554/http://fightnetwork.com/news/9731:arianny-celeste-makes-top-99-most-desirable-women-list/ |archive-date=2014-08-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

